            "game-obj": "Sources",
            "name": "Monster Core pg. 316",
            "type": "link"
          },
          "name": "Monster Core",
          "page": 316,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "Each member of this family of venomous snakes has long, hinged fangs that inject potent venom into their prey. Different vipers inject different types of venom, which might result in paralysis, extreme pain and swelling, blood clotting, or even the sudden stopping of the victim's heart.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
